  <!-- Síntesis de la actividad -->
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="synthesis-actividad-titulo"/></title>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <q>¿Por qué 100 y 200 aparecen en ambos conteos?</q>  (You say 100 and 200 when you are counting by tens or hundreds. You can think of 100 as 10 tens or 200 as 20 tens. 100 and 200 are multiples of 10 and multiples of 100.)
      </li>
    </ul>
  </paragraphs>


